SubjectLoran-C Station, Williams Lake B.C. 1976 Termination of Treaty (US) #7
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to terminate for Canada the EXCHANGE OF NOTES between Canada and the United States of America providing for the Establishment, Maintenance and Operation of a Loran-C Transmitting Station at Williams Lake, B.
